profile: The ReStore Home Improvement Warehouse offers new and used affordable materials for renovators, homeowners, small landlords, cottagers, and others.
products: We carry new and used building materials such as doors, windows, kitchen cabinets, lighting, plumbing, flooring, furniture, d
services: We dismantle your old kitchen or bathroom, or remove windows, doors and other usable items
specialities:
Our Community and Environment benefit by diverting thousands of tons of construction and household materials away from landfills.

You benefit from the opportunity of purchasing products at discounts of 30-75% off retail prices.

Our Partner Families benefit since the revenues generated by the Hamilton ReStore fund all administrative and operational costs at Habita for Humanity Hamilton. As a result, 100% of every financial donation made to Habitat Hamilton goes toward building homes!
